sentences: gobbinjr, the stage name of musician Emma Witmer, is an American indie pop musician from New York City.
Emma Witmer grew up in Wisconsin.
Emma Witmer began releasing music as a student at New York University.
Witmer released her first full-length album titled Manalang on Yellow K Records.
In 2016, Witmer released her first EP titled vom night.
In 2018, Witmer released her second full-length album and first on the record label Topshelf Records.
